#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Introduction
#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is a library which provides translation of the OpenFOAM data 
( Open Source CFD Toolbox, see http://sourceforge.net/projects/foam/ )
to the native VTK representation ( Visualization Toolkit, see http://www.vtk.org/ )
The intial code came from corresponding OpenFOAM "foamToVTK" command line 
utitlity. The initial goal to develop this utility was to be able post-process
the OpenFOAM data on the fly (without intermediate conversion to the files).


#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation
#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

See the INSTALL file for more information about installing of foam2vtk
utility.

